Wan Daniel yang geram dengan kejadian itu, telah pergi memarahi Akasyah kerana menyebabkan Suhana terancam. Sedangkan Akasyah yang tak tahu apa-apa, tak mampu membela diri. Demi menenangkan Wan Daniel, Akasyah akhirnya berjanji tiak akan mendekati Suhana lagi, jika kehadirannya mengancam Suhana.

programme.desc: Cansu dan Deniz terkejut apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa Ezgi pergi ke Gcek dengan zgr mengikut perjanjian. programme.title: Aroma Masak S3 Ep02
programme.desc: Tak tahu nak masak apa hari ni? Bosan makan diluar? Jom memasak bersama selebriti kesayangan anda dalam Aroma Masak yang dihoskan oleh Syafie Naswip dan tetamu jemputannya, Atu Zero.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep06
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam (Angah) dan Mizan (Along) dua beradik dari satu keluarga. Nizam lulusan luar negeri, bekerjaya, baru berkahwin dan baru juga bercerai. Hubungan Nizam dan Mizan tidak mesra sangat. ibu bapa mereka juga memelihara Hani, sebagai adik angkat. Kini, Hani seorang gadis, selain sangat disayangi ibu bapa mereka, Mizan pula mencintainya. Jalinan percintaan mereka juga direstui ibu bapa mereka, cuma Nizam terpaksa menangguhkan perkahwinan mereka sekurang-kurangnya 3 tahun kerana melanjutkan pelajaran keluar negara. Hani yang baik sahsiahnya dan berbudi pekerti, pandai mengemas rumah tangga memahaminya dan sanggup menunggu. Di hari ketibaan Nizam pulang, ibu bapanya telah menetapkan sebagai hari perkahwinan Nizam dan Hani. Selain majlis telah siap, tetamu juga telah dijemput, tiba-tiba sehari sebelum majlis berlangsung, Nizam meminta majlis dibatalkan dengan alasan dia telah berkahwin 5 bulan lalu. Di hari itu, Mizan juga pulang sebagai meraikan majlis adiknya, lalu ibu bapanya mencadangkan Mizan menggantikan tempat Nizam. Mizan agak terkejut dan tidak bersetuju walau pun dirayu demi menutup maruah keluarga. Sementara itu Hani amat berduka, tetapi sebelah malamnya Hani berubah hati semata-mata demi maruah keluarga lalu merayu beberapa kali kepada Mizan mengambilnya sebagai isteri. Mizan bukan sahaja menolak permintaan Hani, sebaliknya mencerca Hani yang dianggap tidak malu. Hani pula terus berdoa. Di awal pagi hari majlis, Mizan berubah hati dan bersetuju. Majlis perkahwinan Mizan dan Hani serta jamuan berjalan lancar. Di sebelah petangnya. Nizam dan isterinya, Shela juga tiba dan mereka dijangka akan tinggal di situ beberapa ketika.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep22
programme.desc: zgr sangat terharu kerana semua yang dia lalui kebelakangan ini dan memutuskan untuk berehat dan pergi ke hutan untuk mengosongkan fikirannya. Tetapi detik damainya di sana tidak bertahan lama, Ezgi, Ozan dan Deniz pergi mencarinya. Mereka semua mempunyai hari yang menyeronokkan bersama. zgr mengambil kekuatannya daripada Ezgi dalam setiap negatif yang dia alami. Setiap saat dia berkongsi dengannya, dia menyedari bahawa dia tidak boleh tanpanya dan melamar Ezgi. Ezgi akhirnya menjalani impiannya, mencari cinta sejati. Dia mengiyakan cadangannya untuk bahagia selamanya dengan zgr.

programme.desc: Saksikan bagaimana seorang selebriti mengisi hari cuti mereka dengan bermacam aktiviti-aktiviti menarik. Dihoskan oleh Asmawi, anda akan mengenali lebih lanjut kisah kehidupan dan karier tetamu undangan kali ini, Qi Razali.

programme.title: Dapur Bujang Leftovers S2 Ep01
programme.desc: Untuk episod kali ini Chef Naem menghasilkan Nasi Lemak Goreng bersama Ayam Rempah & Tauhu Goreng Ayam Kari untuk disajikan kepada penonton. Jom saksikan!

programme.title: Destinasi Bajet S5 Ep10
programme.desc: Dengan bajet yang minimum untuk penginapan, makan minum dan cenderahati untuk tiga hari dua malam ikuti pengembaraan cara destinasi bajet. Bersama Zetty Nabila, ikuti pemgembaraan ke Perlis.

programme.title: Rojak S7 Ep10
programme.desc: "Rojak adalah sebuah rancangan yang membawa pelbagai jenis informasi yang mendedahkan orang awam kepada benda yang mereka tidak biasanya akan cuba dari eksperimen sosial, D.I.Y. dan lain-lain lagi. Dihoskan oleh Leaism."

programme.title: Lubuk S2 Ep03
programme.desc: Rancangan khas yang akan membawa anda ke tempat menarik dari sungai hinggalah ke tempat tersembunyi untuk memancing. Kali ni, kita ke lubuk memancing di sekitar daerah Serendah bersama Joe Aziz.

programme.title: Huru Hara S14 Ep18
programme.desc: Di hoskan oleh Anas Ridzuan, Huru Hara kali ini pasti membuatkan anda terhibur sambil bergelak ketawa. Dalam episod ini kita santai santai bersama barisan artis yang terdiri daripada Bidin Al-Zaifa, Atikah Suhaime, Syuk Sahar dan Katrina Roshan.

programme.title: Girls Only S9 Ep06
programme.desc: Girls Only musim terbaru menampilkan 2 pengacara baru iaitu Leiasm dan Aqilah Azali yang akan berkongsi dengan anda tentang solekkan, dandanan rambut, pemakaian hijab dan juga akan berborak santai bersama tetamu undangan dengan topik yang menarik. Episod kali ini kita bersama Kaseh, anak kepada pelakon Azhar Sulaiman, dengan topik nepotisme.

programme.title: Terbaik Dari Jalanan S1 Ep03
programme.desc: Ikuti Suffren dan Banni dalam jelajah mereka menikmati makanan-makanan terbaik dari gerai, warung dan kedai kaki lima. Kali ini, mereka akan pergi ke Nasi Lemak Maklong, 20 Laman Cafe, Babypancake Bergegau dan DCabin Satay Kajang.

programme.title: Bakar S12 Ep03
programme.desc: Episod kali ini, Chef Kim akan berkongsi dengan penonton, cara membuat Nasi Mentai dan juga Kek Teh Hijau & Kacang Merah

programme.title: Ronda Roda S2 Ep01
programme.desc: Bersama pengacara, Azizul Ammar akan memandu uji kereta Subaru Forester dan juga mengetahui kisah Hanif dan motornya Harley Davidson Sportster.

programme.title: Nak Dengar Cerita Hantu Ep.3 Ep3
programme.desc: Mengisahkan rachel yang di bunuh dengan kejam oleh david dan kawan-kawannya. Rachel di bunuh demi menutupi salah guna kuasa david di dalam syarikat. Roh rachel yang tak tenteram merayau mencari pembunuh dia sehingga dia bertemu ke empat-empat lelaki tersebut. Seorang demi seorang mendapat pembalasan dendam oleh Rachel dan mati. Roh Rachel yang tak tenteram kembali membalas dendam pada setiap pembunuhnya. Selepas sepuluh tahun Rachel berjaya melepaskan semua dendamnya dengan kematian David.

programme.title: Bohsia Jangan Pilih Jalan Hitam
programme.desc: Bohsia: Jangan Pilih Jalan Hitam berkisarkan dua gadis, Tasha (Nabila Huda) dan Amy (Salina Saibi). Tanpa pendidikan tinggi dan didikan yang sewajarnya, kedua-duanya terjebak dalam dunia perlumbaan motor haram - satu keputusan mengubah hidup mereka selama-lamanya.

programme.title: KL Special Forces
programme.desc: Dua kumpulan pontianak, kedua-duanya keturunan Raja Bersiong, tidak lagi memakan darah manusia. Mereka sebaliknya menggantikannya dengan darah sintetik.

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep9
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Ryan berjaya memujuk Nasha dan Mak Jah bergambar. Gambar ini ditunjukkan kepada Dato' Amir. Ryan dibayar ganjaran RM50 ribu kerana berjaya mengesan Mak Jah. Mereka juga menyewa rumah lain untuk Mak Jah. Dalam kes berasingan, Farish sebagai bodyguard bersama Adam meneruskan latihan persilatan dengan datuknya. Perhubungan Adam dengan Hanis semakin mesra. Danial sebagai bodyguard Eliza telah mendapat rahsia Rashid dan Amran. Mereka pernah bersamasama melakukan penculikan ke atas Eliza. Dengan sebab itu Eliza mengambil keputusan tidak lagi mahu berhubung dengan Rashid, Amran pula telah diberhentikan kerja. Rahul sebagai bodyguard Maya memberi amaran kepada Mikhail supaya tidak lagi berjumpa dengan Boboy tetapi Boboy masih berkeras mahu berjumpa dengan ayahnya Mikhail. Diakhir episod, Eliza diculik oleh Amran semasa Rahul bodyguardnya keluar mengambil barang yang tertinggal dari dalam kereta

programme.title: Desolasi
programme.desc: Mengisahkan mengenai Aiman seorang pelukis remaja yang mencari jawapan dalam persoalan kehidupan selepas melalui pelbagai ujian dan dugaan dalam kehidupan sehariannya sehingga membuatkan dirinya hilang arah.

programme.title: Nak Dengar Cerita Hantu Ep.2 Ep2
programme.desc: Sepasang suami isteri iaitu Faizal dan Yana telah kehilangan anak perempuan mereka, Naily. Faizal membawa Yana berpindah ke sebuah rumah yang terletak di dalam dusun dan semenjak itu Yana sering melihat bayangan Naily.

programme.title: Usop Wilcha Meghonjang Makhluk Muzium
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang pihak sebuah muzium yang menganjurkan pameran hantu-hantu dunia dalam usaha menarik orang ramai kembali datang ke muzium. Penganjuran pameran hantu dunia ini tanpa disedaridi rancang oleh pihak tertentu dalam usaha untuk menghidupkan Count Dracula. Kehidupan abadi yang diinginkan oleh Dracula ini pasti akan menyebabkan keadaan negara menjadi huru-hara. Bagaimanapun, rancangan licik kumpulan ini disedari oleh patung-patung tokoh lama yang mempunyai semangat untuk memastikan rancanga ini gagal. Perak Man, Sultan Melaka, Bendahara Tun Perpatih Putih, Datuk Maharaja Lela bersama siPutum terpaksa berkomunikasi dengan orang luar yang mereka boleh percayai bagi menggagalkan rancangan jahat kumpulan itu.

programme.title: Double Barrel
programme.desc: Mengenai pasangan muda yang miskin bekerja sebagai pembunuh upahan sehingga mereka diberi tugasan terbaru untuk menghapuskan abang isteri sendiri yang memaksa mereka lari dan bersembunyi daripada kumpulan itu untuk menyelamatkan diri dan bayi mereka.

programme.title: Budak Magik Ep3
programme.desc: Episod 10 memaparkan kisah bagaimana rahsia Hariman, Salim dan Sohot terlibat dalam rompakan batu permata terbongkar apabila Haikal terdengar perbualan mereka. Sementara itu ibu Maira yang pada mulanya teruja apabila diberitahu batu milik Maira bernilai RM 15 ribu bertukar kecewa setelah mendapat tahu batu itu palsu. Manakala Hariman dilihat mengekori dan mengintip setiap pergerakan Imran, Haikal dan Maira.

programme.title: Jangan Ikut Aku Ep8
programme.desc: Akil pulang kerumah dari bengkel dan dapati saka Mayang Kasturi sedang menunggunya. Mayang Kasturi minta tolong Akil mencari rantai miliknya yang sekarang ini dalam milik seorang perempuan yang berambut panjang dan suka memakai baju kebaya. Mayang Kasturi mahu rantai itu untuk membolehnya pulang ke habitat asalnya dan berjanji tidak akan mengganggu Akil atau manusia lain lagi. Akil ingin tahu cerita rantai itu. Mayang Kasturi mengguna kuasa sakanya menidurkan Akil dan dalam tidur dia terlihat Mayang Kasturi berkawan dengan seorang gadis bernama Ally. Sejak berkawan dengan Mayang Kasturi, Ally berubah sikap dan suka melawan dan tidak mendengar cakap ibunya lagi. Bomoh Tok Misai berjaya menghalau Mayang Kasturi daripada Ally dan telah mengambil rantai saka milik Mayang Kasturi. Mayang Kasturi mahu semula rantai itu. Akil berjanji akan membantu dan secara kebetulan dia terlihat Siti, kerani di bengkelnya memakai rantai tersebut. Akil membuat tawaran untuk membeli rantai itu daripada Siti tetapi gagal. Akhirnya Akil berjaya memiliki rantai itu apabila Siti tertinggal di bilik mandi. Rantai itu diserah kepada Mayang Kasturi yang berjanji tidak akan mengganggu Akil lagi.

programme.title: Haq
programme.desc: "Haq" ialah sebuah filem aksi mengenai perjuangan antara kebaikan dan kejahatan.Haq (Zul Huzaimy) dan Bad (Adi Putra) dikurniakan kuasa istimewa.Bad, yang menjadi anak angkat oleh keluarga Haq, mempunyai kebencian yang mendalam terhadap Haq.Dia menggunakan kuasanya untuk mencemarkan nama baik Haq.Bagaimanapun, Haq enggan menggunakan kuasanya untuk menghalang Bad sehingga dia mendapati dirinya terperangkap oleh yang terakhir.

programme.title: Nak Dengar Cerita Hantu Ep.2 Ep2
programme.desc: Sepasang suami isteri iaitu Faizal dan Yana telah kehilangan anak perempuan mereka, Naily. Faizal membawa Yana berpindah ke sebuah rumah yang terletak di dalam dusun dan semenjak itu Yana sering melihat bayangan Naily.

programme.title: Reunion
programme.desc: Seorang wanita hamil pulang ke rumah keluarga datuk dan neneknya yang baru meninggal dunia untuk meluangkan masa bersama ibunya yang terasing. Apa yang bermula sebagai perjumpaan bertukar menjadi menakutkan.

programme.title: You Saka.. Pergi Jauh Jauh Ep3
programme.desc: Episod Pertama cereka komedi seram disusuli dengan kepercayaan khurafat ini berkisar kepada personaliti Nia. Nia sebagai setiausaha syarikat milik seorang Datin Salina yang amat menyukainya hingga bercadang untuk dijodohkan kepada anak lelakinya. Ibu Nia dikampung, sedang sakit dijagai oleh Roslan, bapa saudaranya (Pak Lang). Nia mempercayai dia wajar menyeru puteri yang sesekali Nia akan lakukan bertujuan melindunginya dan juga sebagai amalan turun temurunnya selama ini. Jika tidak dilakukan, saka berbentuk syaitan akan menggangguinya. Ada sebab-sebab bahawa ibunya memiliki saka dan kematiannya bererti saka itu cuba mempengaruhi warisnya iaitu Nia. Nia tinggal dengan Shasa dan sepupu Shasa iaitu, Adrus adalah 'boy friend' Nia. Adrus sedang menceburi kerjaya dalam bidang paranormal, merupakan anak Ibrahim seorang bomoh. Ketika ibu Nia meninggal dunia dia belum ketahui. Sementara itu, semasa pengembumian ibunya berlaku juga kekecuhan iaitu muncul lembaga putih (berbentuk manusia - wanita). Selain dari itu, sesekali saka Gelam berbentuk syaitan (hitam jalur hijau) mengganggui Nia, 'boy friend'nya dan pernah bersama lembaga putih mengganggui bomoh Ibrahim.

programme.title: Superbike
programme.desc: Ia berkisar tentang kehidupan seharian sekumpulan penunggang motosikal superbike yang menggelar kumpulan mereka sebagai 'Pirate Bikers' dan diketuai oleh Bugs (Kamal Adli). Berlumba-lumba di jalanan, kejar-mengejar, berkonvoi dan disaman oleh polis telah menjadi rasa masam dalam kehidupan mereka yang berkongsi minat yang sama.

programme.title: Desolasi
programme.desc: Mengisahkan mengenai Aiman seorang pelukis remaja yang mencari jawapan dalam persoalan kehidupan selepas melalui pelbagai ujian dan dugaan dalam kehidupan sehariannya sehingga membuatkan dirinya hilang arah.

Roh Rachel yang tak tenteram kembali membalas dendam pada setiap pembunuhnya. Selepas sepuluh tahun Rachel berjaya melepaskan semua dendamnya dengan kematian David.

programme.title: Mother Gamer
programme.desc: Untuk menghalang anak lelaki kesayangannya yang menyertai kejohanan E-sukan, dia memutuskan untuk menubuhkan pasukannya sendiri untuk mengalahkannya dan menghapuskan impiannya untuk menjadi pemain permainan profesional.

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep10
programme.desc: Mengisahkan semasa Eliza bersama bodyguardnya Danial dia nyaris dilanggar. Mereka syak Amran seorang kakitangan Eliza melakukan cubaan tersebut. Hubungan percintaan Eliza dengan Rashid masih berterusan. Farish sebagai bodyguard, masih meneruskan jagaan keselamatan kepada Adam. Dia beberapa kali menyelamatkan Adam dari dipukul oleh Zack dan rakan kumpulannnya. Adam dikatakan membocor rahsia kumpulan kepada polis sehingga ada di kalangan mereka yang telah tertangkap. Ryan bodyguard Datin Maziah, dia menunjukkan photo perhubungan Datin Maziah dengan Badrul kepada Dato Zailani. Akhirnya Dato Zailani menceraikan Datin Maziah. Di akhir episod, Amran melihat Rashid berbaik-baik dengan Eliza, dia memberi amaran kepada Rashid untuk membocorkan rahsia mereka kepada Eliza sekiranya tidak memberi wang kepadanya.

programme.title: Felak
programme.desc: Seher, yang kehilangan bapanya pada usia muda, mengalami masalah psikologi. Erhan cintakan Seher sejak kecil, berkahwin dengan Nilay. Seher sangat cemburu dengan Nilay. Seher, yang mengalami gangguan saraf yang berterusan, menjadi kecewa. Nilay dan Erhan berpendapat keadaan Seher ini ada kaitan dengan penyakitnya. Tetapi ada sesuatu yang mereka tidak tahu. Seher telah menggunakan mantra untuk membalas dendam kepada Nilay.

programme.title: The Cave
programme.desc: Apabila pasukan bola sepak remaja yang terdiri daripada 12 lelaki, berumur 11-16, dan jurulatih mereka berusia 25 tahun terperangkap jauh di dalam gua di Utara Thailand, beribu-ribu sukarelawan dan tentera dari seluruh dunia bersatu dalam perlumbaan melawan masa untuk mencari mereka . Sebaik sahaja kanak-kanak lelaki itu ditemui hidup sepuluh hari kemudian, satu-satunya jalan keluar ialah berenang selama lima jam yang mustahil yang hanya penyelam gua yang pakar boleh bertahan. Di Ireland, juruelektrik kilang kapal terbang dan penyelam gua rekreasi Jim Warny menerima panggilan: "Berapa lama lagi anda boleh berada di sini?" Tiba di Thailand, Jim melangkah keluar dari pesawat dan masuk ke dalam gua - misi tiga hari bermata pisau sedang dijalankan. Berdasarkan peristiwa sebenar, THE CAVE menceritakan kisah mendebarkan tentang misi menyelamat antarabangsa terbesar pada zaman moden, dari perspektif unik lelaki dan wanita yang menghadapi keputusan hidup dan mati dan mempamerkan keazaman dan pengorbanan yang tidak mementingkan diri sendiri, yang memuncak dengan keputusan yang berjaya menentang semua kemungkinan.

programme.desc: Di tengah-tengah pelanggaran undang-undang dan rasuah, detektif polis legenda Khun Pan menyertai kumpulan penyamun yang menggerunkan tetapi bergelut dengan kesetiaannya.

programme.title: Rien Pembunuh Berantai
programme.desc: Rein, seorang lelaki muda dengan masa lalu yang kelam, adalah pelaku kepada mangsa yang dicacatkan yang ditemui di dalam beg pakaian. Dia bekerja di sebuah syarikat swasta dan disenangi ramai orang, tetapi masa lalunya yang kelam membuatkan dia trauma. Dia dibuli oleh kawan-kawannya, ibunya mempunyai hubungan sulit dengan lelaki lain, dan gadis yang dia cintai mengkhianati lelaki lain. Suatu hari, Rein dikehendaki polis dan kini menjadi buruan polis.

programme.title: Marai Mugam
programme.desc: Filem komedi Tamil Malaysia arahan Sara. R fdam (RMS), dibintangi oleh ahli pasukan RMS. programme.title: Nak Dengar Cerita Hantu Ep.3 Ep3
programme.desc: Mengisahkan rachel yang di bunuh dengan kejam oleh david dan kawan-kawannya. Rachel di bunuh demi menutupi salah guna kuasa david di dalam syarikat. Roh rachel yang tak tenteram merayau mencari pembunuh dia sehingga dia bertemu ke empat-empat lelaki tersebut. Seorang demi seorang mendapat pembalasan dendam oleh Rachel dan mati. Roh Rachel yang tak tenteram kembali membalas dendam pada setiap pembunuhnya. Selepas sepuluh tahun Rachel berjaya melepaskan semua dendamnya dengan kematian David.

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep11
programme.desc: Mengisahkan semasa Eliza bersama bodyguardnya Danial dia nyaris dilanggar. Mereka syak Amran seorang kakitangan Eliza melakukan cubaan tersebut. Hubungan percintaan Eliza dengan Rashid masih berterusan. Farish sebagai bodyguard, masih meneruskan jagaan keselamatan kepada Adam. Dia beberapa kali menyelamatkan Adam dari dipukul oleh Zack dan rakan kumpulannnya. Adam dikatakan membocor rahsia kumpulan kepada polis sehingga ada di kalangan mereka yang telah tertangkap. Ryan bodyguard Datin Maziah, dia menunjukkan photo perhubungan Datin Maziah dengan Badrul kepada Dato Zailani. Akhirnya Dato Zailani menceraikan Datin Maziah. Di akhir episod, Amran melihat Rashid berbaik-baik dengan Eliza, dia memberi amaran kepada Rashid untuk membocorkan rahsia mereka kepada Eliza sekiranya tidak memberi wang kepadanya.

programme.title: Janda Meletup
programme.desc: Rosnah, seorang janda muda cuba dipikat oleh Kamil yang tertarik dengannya namun gagal. Samad yang berasal dari Kuala Lumpur pergi ke kampung untuk mencari pembantu rumah dan bertemu Rosnah yang ingin bekerja dengannya. Kamil yang kecewa pergi ke Kuala Lumpur untuk berjumpa Rosnah selain tekadnya yang ingin bekerja dan mengahwini Rosnah. Suatu insiden terjadi menyebabkan Rosnah dan Kamil berganding bahu untuk menyelamatkan Samad.

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Kisah seorang graduan universiti bekerja sebagai budak pejabat yang pada suatu hari didatangi oleh seekor monyet cerdik tersesat ke rumahnya. Suatu hari berlaku krisis di pejabatnya. Budak pejabat itu perlu segera mencari jalan untuk menyelesaikan masalah dan dalam proses itu hampir membahayakan nyawanya sendiri. Dengan bantuan monyet tersebut, dia berjaya mengatasi banyak masalah dan berjaya menyelamatkan pekerjaannya.

programme.title: Cikgu Romantik

programme.title: Pro on their Speciality (T) Ep970
programme.desc: A popular educational documentary programs that record and reports all sorts of business stories all over the land of Taiwan

programme.title: The Comeback
programme.desc: Uncle Hua is a retired agent who owns an antique shop on an old street. When the old street is forcibly demolished by the local Green Dragon Gang one day, Uncle Huas hidden identity is accidentally revealed, and he is pursued by a mysterious organization headed by Ah Jie. A fatal duel has just begun!

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. While things seem to be falling apart, this dinner may well be an opportunity to mend relations.

programme.title: God of Gamblers 2
programme.desc: A new chapter of the highly successful "God of Gamblers". The legend's disciple Andy Lau is now rising in the gambling world as the "Knight of Gamblers"; clashing with another gambling icon, the wild psychic Stephen Chow (aka "Saint of Gamblers") who wants to follow the God. They mix like oil and water in a series of tricks and mishaps, but are forced to join hands against their master's nemesis on the gambling table.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Shanghai
programme.desc: Ma Yong Zhen moves to Shanghai in the hope of becoming rich but ends up having to use his kung fu skills to survive and take revenge against the gang who killed his brother.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Hong Kong
programme.desc: This is a story of ICAC investigators fighting against rampant corruption in early 1970s Hong Kong. A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC to investigate their collusion and fight against corruption, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: Hidden Heroine
programme.desc: A drug cartel is entrenched in the Dong Zhou area. Mei Jing of the Thunderbolt Womens Commando Unit, leads her team to attack the drug base, but they are being ambushed and the identity of Meis father as an undercover is exposed. After a fierce battle, Mei and her team manage to successfully defeat the drug cartel and rescue her father.

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: Mosaic, an urban sketcher, is suffering from ALS and wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. When Mosaic reunites with his old classmate Angelfish, whom he has a crush on since primary school, he asks her to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day. Will Angelfish say yes?

programme.title: Think Big Big
programme.desc: Moon is a plus-sized girl working happily as a mascot at a theme park. That is until one day she accidentally joins a weight loss competition, with her remarkable transformation turning her into the "Nations Goddess". Netizens have their eyes glued on her, turning her life upside down, and Moon has to find a way to be happy again.

programme.title: Blind War
programme.desc: Former SWAT captain Dong Gu suffers traumatic visual loss during a failed mission for which he is forced to take responsibility. He manages to get over and adapt to the situation with his daughters company, until his nemesis appears and puts his daughter in danger. Despite being blind, Dong Gu must fight to save his daughter.

programme.title: Acting Out of Love
programme.desc: Wei Hung Jen is a struggling actor who gets fired but finds a job behind the scene. Hui Hsin, the associate producer, must write a script for a love story so as to get a reference letter to study scriptwriting overseas. As Jen falls for Hui, he invites her out on a date as a research for her script and they start acting out of love.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon (2020)
programme.desc: In 1960s Hong Kong, rookie cop Xu Le cracks a robbery but gets demoted instead, as this offends a corrupt inspector. Xu meets a rich girl Bai who falls instantly in love with him one day. Will he break up with his childhood girlfriend for Bai so as to climb the social ladder, and how does Xu eventually become one of Hong Kongs legendary detective?

programme.title: Call Me Agent
programme.desc: Miu Ling dreams of becoming a secret agent. Even though it seems impossible, she still harbours such a dream and hopes that it will soon come true. One day, Miu Ling rescues an injured secret agent who promises to make her his apprentice. From then on, her life is turned upside down and she goes onto a roller-coaster of madcap adventures.

programme.title: Hand Rolled Cigarette
programme.desc: A retired British-Chinese soldier becomes a target in a triad manhunt when he takes in a young South Asian man who carries a bag of stolen drugs. Forced to live together, the two men transcend conflicts and cultural differences to form a beautiful friendship in this poignant tale of loyalty and brotherhood.

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: A 28-year-old IT geek has only been in love once. Surprisingly, he ends up getting romantically involved with five different women this year and the one thing they have in common is that they all live in far flung areas of Hong Kong. After taking five intensive relationship courses within these 365 days, will he find the-one?

programme.title: A Writer's Odyssey
programme.desc: Based on a novel of the same name, this is the story about a father who must kill a novelist in order to find his missing daughter. Through a strange twist of fate, the fantasy world of the novel begins to impact life in the real world.

Chow Mo Wan encounters many women in his life but is touched by none after he lost his true love. Following an encounter one day, he decides to write a fiction titled 2046 which takes place at Room 2046. Nothing ever changes at Room 2046, and people go there to find their lost memories.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 2
programme.desc: In this sequel, Zhang Wu Ji successfully rescued the Six Major sects at Dadu. Nevertheless, the quest for the Dragon Sabre continues as Wu Ji and his three girlfriends set sail for Ice Fire Island. After a series of vicious fights, they finally unveil the secret behind the Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre.

programme.title: The Rookies
programme.desc: An extreme sports lover accidentally gets involved in an illegal trading activity by international crime syndicates. Led by international special agent Bruce, he forms an amateur unit with a police officer, an inventor and a doctor to fight the crime syndicates together, leading to a series of thrilling and hilarious adventures.

programme.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
programme.desc: Donnie Yen plays a Hong Kong police officer who is highly skilled in martial arts but balloons to more than 200 pounds after his fianc left him. His boss can only assign simple tasks to him like escorting a criminal to Japan, but can he complete it?

programme.title: Dragon Master: Dragon Spell
programme.desc: The Dragon King is locked in a seal by the Dragon Master for 500 years, and his daughter must travel back in time to 500 years ago to kill the Dragon Master, in order to reverse the act. Little did she know that the Dragon King and Dragon Master were close friends back then

programme.title: A Witness out of the Blue
programme.desc: The police suspects that a jewel thief, found dead in his unit with all stolen goods missing, is killed by his gang leader. They also found the crime to be related to a jewel robbery many months ago, with the robbers involved being killed off one by one. In this complicated case, the polices only witness is a talking parrot from the crime scene.

programme.title: Book of Love
programme.desc: A casino PR in Macau receives a classic novel 84, Charing Cross Road. She sends back the novel with a letter to where it came from as she does not like it. A real estate agent in California receives the novel and as it does not belong to him, he sends it back with a letter as well. The two form a relationship after all the back and forth.

programme.title: Seobok
programme.desc: Former secret agent Ki Hun is entrusted with a secret mission to escort the first human clone, Seobok, to a safe place. Seobok, who possesses a life-preserving DNA that could save humanity, explores the outside world with Ki Hun for the first time but they are both chased and claimed as terrorists by CIA. How can Ki Hun protect Seobok from danger?

programme.title: Distinction
programme.desc: A music teacher in a special needs school, an underachiever from an elite school, and a rebellious teenager with a handicapped brother take part in a campus musical for various reasons. Little did they know that this turns out to be a journey of self-discovery.

programme.title: Love and Let Love!
programme.desc: Cliff proposes to his girlfriend Terry but is killed in a car accident before she says yes. Terry is devastated and inconsolable. When Cliff's ghost returns, they seem to go back to their good old days. However, Cliff is determined to help Terry get over his death and start anew.

programme.title: VR Fighter
programme.desc: Bodyguard Long Wei has posttraumatic stress disorder after his wife's death. One day, he encounters Amy who works for a VR technology firm and is invited for a new product test. After the test, Long Wei becomes the firms VR fighter and dons the newly invented armour. However, as mysterious armed men break in, a fierce battle has just begun...

programme.title: Bodies at Rest
programme.desc: When three armed criminals barge into a morgue, a forensic doctor and his student must fight with their lives to stop the criminals from obtaining a bullet from inside a corpse that is a key piece of evidence in a deadly crime.

programme.title: My Country, My Parents
programme.desc: Set in 4 different eras in China, the 4-part anthology about home and country is directed by Wu Jing, Zhang Zi Yi, Xu Zheng and Shen Teng, who also star in their own story. The movie depicts how the fathers forge ahead through the struggle of times, defending strong family ties and passing on the fighting spirit through generations.

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: Wolf Pack
programme.desc: The Wolf Pack squad led by Lao Diao, is a foreign-based team that specializes in overseas security jobs. In one of the missions, the squad discovers that a terrorist force is planning to destroy the countrys energy source. Lao Diao is now entrusted with the task of leading his squad to fight back. Can the Wolf Pack save the day?

programme.title: Europe Raiders
programme.desc: Mr Lin and Miss Wang are the two top bounty hunters in the business, and are searching for the destructive missile Hand of God to prove who is the better bounty hunter. They soon realize they are not the only ones after the missile. Will Lin and Wang put their differences aside and work together in search for the Hand of God?

programme.title: The Wandering Earth II
programme.desc: In this prequel, humans build enormous engines on the Earths surface to find a new home when the sun is burning out. In the dangerous universe, a group of young people has to step forward once again to fight in the critical battle to save the Earth.

programme.title: The Blood Brothers
programme.desc: The friendship of three sworn brothers, Zhang, Huang and Ma breaks when Ma gives in to corruption and falls for Huang's wife, eventually leading to a bloody ending.

programme.title: Rear Entrance
programme.desc: Mrs Xu is childless and watches a lonely little girl playing at the rear entrance from afar every day. She warmly nurtures the girl and even adopts her from her uncaring parent. The girl brings happiness to the Xus until her long lost mother appears one day and to make her happy, Mrs Xu reluctantly lets the girl reunite with her mother.

programme.title: The Crimson Charm
programme.desc: In attempting to rescue some innocent people, swordsman Chiang Tzu-chao (Fang Mien) slays the son of Tsao Kang (Wang Hsia), leader of the ruthless Crimson Charm gang.The enraged father promises vengeance on the day of Chiang's 60th birthday...

programme.title: Lovers Blades
programme.desc: Forbidden love and magical weapons are at the centre of this enjoyable martial arts comedy. A reunited couple must recover the titular swords and avenge a murder from their past!

programme.title: Return to the 36th Chamber
programme.desc: The second film of the trilogy, Gordon Liu plays Zhou Ren Jie, a man who impersonates a monk in order to learn kung fu in Shaolin, and eventually creates his own Shaolin style of scaffolding kung fu.

programme.title: Sunset
programme.desc: Teenage heart-throbs Ching Li and Paul Chin Pei come across like Annette Funicello and Frankie Avalon in the musical Sunset, a musical romp that plays similar to one of Hollywood's famous "Beach Party" movies. A car load of girls meets a car load of boys, and Ching and Paul ultimately fall in love. Yet the film takes an acrid twist and turns out to be more like a Shakespearian tragedy than a beach-babe party.

programme.title: Have Sword Will Travel
programme.desc: When the head of a manor loses his kung fu skills, he enlists his nephew and his fianc to help escort gold to the capital. The duo run into a mysterious knight along the way and they join hands to prevent bandits from stealing the gold.

programme.title: Tiger Killer
programme.desc: Wu Song is appointed as chief constable after killing a tiger with his bare hands when drunk. The wife of his brother Wu Da Lang, seduces Wu Song but gets rejected by him, and engages in an affair with a rich man. They poison Wu Da Lang when he finds out about their affair. To avenge his brothers death, Wu Song kills both of them.

programme.title: One Way Only
programme.desc: Danny is a motorbike workshop owner, once was a renowned motorcycle racer, but were seriously injured in an illegal race. Mai, student of Danny, wins a race in Macau under Danny's help. However, because of money and honour, Mai joins illegal races. After knowing this, Li persuades Mai to stop illegal races, but Mai seems cannot find his way out

programme.title: Raw Passions
programme.desc: Mrs Lin's husband and his friend both have affairs with a belly dancer Sasa, and are both blackmailed by her. Sasa is stabbed one day and her brother shows up asking for money. A mysterious man also claims he can offer evidence for cash to help Lins husband. Lin has to unveil the deceit, double-crosses and blackmailing before she is in danger too!

programme.title: The Swordmates
programme.desc: Li asks his swordmate Wang to protect his family while he is away, but Wang rapes his wife and even has his convoy attacked. Li escaped but fears his daughter is still in danger, so he asks the nephew of his master to help protect her

programme.title: The Golden Lion
programme.desc: The Golden Lion is a bandit with good martial arts skills and often robs from the rich to help the poor. He is ambushed and attacked by a gang one night but luckily found help from a master healer, who has to find a way to treat him while they are both being chased by the gang.

programme.title: Carry on Doctors and Nurses
programme.desc: At St. Morant Hospital, a harried but lovely administrator must deal with lusty interns, student nurses, a delirious surgeon, a dissection fiend, a criticizing Commissioner and gross negligence at regular intervals! This comedy is based on the hugely successful British Carry On! film series.

programme.title: Disciples Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Yi is a skilled disciple of the Hong Quan style kung fu who work in a textile mill recommended by his senior, Han. Han warns Yi not to show off his martial arts skill so as to avoid getting into trouble. However, Yi does not listen and eventually gets dangerously involved in the conflict between two opposing textile mills.

programme.title: Song Of Orchid Island
programme.desc: Dr. He moves to the remote Lanyu island off the coast of Taiwan to look for his long lost father, and starts to run a clinic curing islanders who are bitten by the fatal red worms there. He meets Ya Lan who works as a nurse in his clinic and falls in love with him. Things get vicious for Dr. He as a jealous islander plots to get rid of him

programme.title: The 14 Amazons
programme.desc: The Yang family had served their country in Song Dynasty for generations. When General Yang is ambushed and killed during the war in Jin Shan, the grand matriarch led the entire family to take revenge and defend the country.

programme.title: My Son
programme.desc: Kuo, a polices son, blames his father for his mothers death. He has no job, spends time in night clubs and always gets into fights. One night, Kuo rescues Mei from being raped and they become friends. Kuo wants to support Mei and her family so he goes gambling hoping to gain more money but bad luck seems to be following them with tragic outcomes.

programme.title: The Weird Man
programme.desc: During the Three Kingdoms period, a Taoist priest Yu Ji cures many patients with his supernatural powers and is loved by the people. However, the arrogant general Sun Che thinks that Yu Ji bewitches people and orders for him to be beheaded. Subsequently, the spirit of the Yu Ji rises from his dead body and takes revenge on Sun Che.

programme.title: Whose Baby is in the Classroom?
programme.desc: Chen, a male teacher in an all girls high school, is stuck with a baby that isnt his and must take care of it. As he lives on the school grounds, the baby is a source of constant distraction and worry! Luckily, his class warms to the baby and helps him take care of it while he works his charm on Li Ching, an uptight teacher in the same school.

programme.title: All Men are Brothers
programme.desc: This is a sequel to Chang Chehs epic The Water Margin, and follows the patriotic story of seven warriors in the band of 108 outlaws at Mount Liang. The magnificent seven battle against the despotic government officials to save their country.

programme.title: Hong Kong Rhapsody
programme.desc: Hong Kong rhapsody is a musical extravaganza full of song and dance! Peter Chen-Ho stars as a playboy magician who changes his ways after he becomes the guardian of a young singer (Li Ching), the daughter of a deceased magician friend.

programme.title: The Duel of the Century
programme.desc: Liu Yung and Korean "Venom" Sun Chien team up to investigate the martial-art murders of a supposedly mortally wounded swordsman, only to find deception, death, double-dealings, imposters and one deadly duel after another.

programme.title: The Millionaire Chase
programme.desc: It's a fun and wild romp that mixes pleasure with pleasure. A nightclub owner, playboy Peter Chen Ho, has his ways with three sisters while gallivanting across Asia. Each one has a dangling relationship to save - ensuring a series of mishaps and comic moments.

programme.title: Man Of Iron
programme.desc: Chou Lian Huan (Chen Kuan Tai) is good at fist fighting in Shanghai. In order to please a hostess named Chen Ju Fang (Ching Li), he is willing to sacrifice everything and fight against the son of the gang leader in Shanghai. However, is Chous action worth it?

programme.title: The Bloody Escape
programme.desc: Ku is a skilled Kung Fu artist brought up by the bandits and does not agree with the brutal leader of the bandits camp. He rescues Tong, a young lady forced to become the leaders wife, causing both the authorities and bandits to come after them. Ku has to stand up against the bandits that he grew up with so as to start a new life for himself.

programme.title: The Pure and the Evil
programme.desc: Two teen girls, Rose and May, become close friends despite their different social backgrounds. The rich girl May moves to America but returns years later to see Rose, now a beauty queen and bar girl. Rose is immediately attracted to Fangs fianc and their relationship quickly deteriorates when Rose sets out to pursue him

programme.title: The Proud Youth
programme.desc: Ling Hu Chong, a Huashan clans disciple, is assigned to find the successor to the score The Proud One. Ling identifies Ying for the score but finds out that she is the daughter of the evil clans leader. At the same time, he is unwittingly dragged into an epic power struggle between clans, with complicated allegiances and perplexing moralities.

programme.title: Hex Vs Witchcraft
programme.desc: A compulsive gambler with bad luck owes money to a violent gangster boss and trades his wife as down payment, causing her to leave him. As he decides to kill himself, a mysterious old man offers him a proposal to marry the ghost of his dead daughter in exchange for cash and an expensive apartment.

programme.title: Descendant of the Sun
programme.desc: Shi Sheng is adopted by an old carpenter and grows up to possess extraordinary superpowers. One day, he unexpectedly discovers his identity as the son of the solar deity and learns that his power will be lost during solar eclipse. When an evil spirit appears and wreaks havoc, Shi Sheng must beat him in an ultimate duel to save the world.

programme.title: Hex after Hex
programme.desc: Hell may have no fury like a woman scorned, but hell literally, really has no wrath like a lusting ghost scorned! Cult classic director Kuei Chih-hung shoots the works with this amazing horror romance starring muscular "Venom" Lo Meng.

programme.title: Chinatown Kid
programme.desc: After getting into trouble with a local gangster, Chui Ho, a young man, Tam Dong flees to San Francisco and manages to get a job in a restaurant in Chinatown. Tam Dong finds himself embroiled with the gang again while in San Francisco, and has to fight Chui Ho when the two meet again...

programme.title: Sex, Love and Hate
programme.desc: This masterpiece spins three interconnected tales about Hong Kong society's differing views on love and what women want from love. Follow a trio of Hong Kong women as they explore relationships and fulfil their hopes of finding true love.

programme.title: Duel Of Fist
programme.desc: Fan Ke discovers at his fathers deathbed that he has a half-brother, Wenlie, in Thailand. He goes to find Wenlie, who became a boxer to support his sick mother. Following their encounter, the two got involved in the underworld of boxing match gambling.

programme.title: River of Tears
programme.desc: Retired singer Fang lives happily with her husband and son. Tragedy happens when a man from her past returns to haunt her. In an ensuing struggle to free her from his clutches, her husband dies in a car accident. Blamed by her father-in-law for her husbands death, Fang gets chased out of the house and goes back to singing to make a living...

programme.title: The Iron Buddha
programme.desc: After a notorious rapist Xiao kills his master and the entire clan, Han the last surviving disciple, decides to take revenge. He must find the legendary Hulong Blade to counter Xiao's Evil Poisonous Sword, but as Han has never seen Xiao before, he is deceived when Xiao poses as an ally to try and steal his Blade in the process.

programme.title: Expedition with Steve Backshall S2 Ep6

programme.desc: Manzi the Superpack - Head back to the den with the Kakumbi, who are mourning the loss of two pups. Chance upon a hyena den and a lion pride trying to take down a buffalo, then catch up with the Manzi, who are in a standoff with a leopard and a herd of angry elephants.

programme.title: A Wild Year on Earth 1 Ep2
programme.desc: March-April - a Time of Renewal - Travel around the globe to witness the atmospheric shifts that take place in March, from the wave of cherry blossoms that unfold across Japan to the final raft of green sea turtles that arrive on the Great Barrier Reef islands to lay eggs.

programme.title: Alaskan Summer
programme.desc: Alaskan Summer - Nearly 20 hours of sunlight a day feed the season of abundance. Warmth unlocks water from the glaciers, ice caves and waterfalls. programme.title: Zambia Untamed 1 Ep3
programme.desc: The Acacia Loop - As the dry season begins, thousands of animals are making their way to the Acacia Loop. Each must establish their place in the pecking order and avoid the dangerous residents who are all too willing to make a meal of the unwary.

programme.title: Zambia Untamed 1 Ep4
programme.desc: Mvula's Journey - Mvula is the youngest calf in the Madzi family. Temperatures are soaring. Lagoons and waterholes are drying up. This forces Mvula and his family to undertake a long and dangerous journey to the only remaining source of water: the Luangwa River.

programme.title: City Wildlife Rescue 1 Ep8
programme.desc: Join the rescue team as they respond to a call about an opossum stuck in a fence that turns out not to be the kind of animal that plays dead. Inside the center, a goose with a serious foot injury receives physiotherapy before returning to the wild.

programme.title: Mysteries of the Mekong 1 Ep1

programme.title: Wild Castles 1 Ep1

programme.title: Wild Dogs: Pack vs. Pride 2 Ep5

programme.title: A Wild Year on Earth 1 Ep3
programme.desc: May-June - a Time of Volatility - Watch summer unfold in the Northern Hemisphere, while regions close to the equator enter the wet season and Southern Africa goes dry, creating scarcity for some creatures and bounty for others.

programme.title: America's Wild Border: Northern Exposure

programme.desc: A Tale of Two Penguins - At the waters edge a brave group of male penguins gather, preparing to make the dangerous journey ashore. programme.title: Wildest New Zealand 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Untamed West - New Zealands West Coast is like nowhere else on Earth. From glacier-covered mountains to rain-drenched native forests to rough frigid seas, the landscape defies belief. Isolated from the rest of the world, this strip of almost untouched wilderness hides a host of endemic animals. Evolutionary castaways, every one of them is a rare ecological jewel. From alpine parrots and shy penguins to mammal-like kiwis and ancient eels. To survive the conditions the wildlife here has to be hardy, cunning and resourceful. A journey along the West Coast reveals the beauty of this land, and the trials and tribulations of the wildlife that live here.

programme.title: Olivia Ep33

programme.title: Olivia Ep34

programme.title: Olivia Ep35

programme.title: Olivia Ep36

She doesn't have much success, until she manages to make herself disappear for Ian and Julian. They can't figure out how she's done it, but Ian doesn't care. He just wants his big sister back!

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep13
programme.desc: Why Vulture Is Bald - You see there was time when Vulture was not bald. Oh no, Vulture's head was covered in a beautiful crown of golden plumage! Vain Vulture never shut up about her golden feathers and was obsessed about making them as golden as the sun!'. One day Vulture decides to fly up to the sun, but her precious feathers get burnt! Vulture decides to sooth her smoking feathers with golden honey which she steals from the bees. The bees are not pleased and Vulture sticks her head down Aardvark's burrow. However, Aardvark loves feathers all covered in honey and when Vulture surfaces she is as bald as well, as a Vulture! Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep14
programme.desc: Why Giraffe Has A Long Neck - You see there was a time when Giraffe didn't have a long neck. Her neck was all short and stumpy and she was a very delicate eater. All the food in Tinga Tinga seemed to make her tummy go funny. Then one day Lion suggests she try some honey. With the Bees permission, Giraffe tries to lick the honey but it is deep, deep inside the tree. Giraffe squeezes her head into the honey tree and then EEEeeek! Her head gets stuck! Summer, Autumn, Winter pass by with Giraffe's head stuck inside the tree, but she is quite happy because the honey is so delicious. The tree grows and Giraffe's neck gets longer and longer! After a whole year POP!' she manages to pull herself free and from that day on Giraffe has a very long neck and can eat the freshest leaves on the very tops of the trees! Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep15
programme.desc: Why Porcupine Has Quills - You see there was a time when Porcupine didn't have quills, she had the softest coat in all of Tinga Tinga and Jackal wanted it. Despite warnings from all the animals Porcupine allows Jackal to invite her to his cave to keep out of the rain. Porcupine takes off her coat to allow it to dry, but while she sleeps naughty Jackal runs off with it. When she awakes Porcupine is covered in lots of tiny ant bites and they itch and they itch and they itch. Tortoise suggests Elephant squeeze some milk from the Milky Quill bush but Porcupine can't wait anymore and runs into the Quill bushes to relieve her itching. Crash! Crash! Crash! Porcupine crashes through the Quill bushes and emerges covered in spikey quills! The animals can't believe their eyes! But Porcupine is delighted as no beast will ever come near her sensitive skin ever again! Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep16
programme.desc: Why Lizard Always Hides Under Rocks - You see there was a time when Lizard didn't hide under rocks. He would scamper around Tinga Tinga pinching other animals food and keeping it all for himself. Then one day the animals decide to give greedy Lizard a dose of his own medicine. When Lizard realizes the error of his ways he runs and hides under a rock too ashamed to show his face in Tinga Tinga. Tales from Africa.
